form_title.ms_form_title_llm_v1: APPLICATION FOR IMMIGRANT VISA AND ALIEN REGISTRATION

full_text: Screened by NARA, 9/27/2023 OMB APPROVAL NO. 1405-0015 EXPIRES: 9-30-95 ESTIMATED BURDEN: &HOUR APPLICATION FOR IMMIGRANT VISA AND ALIEN REGISTRATION PART I - BIOGRAPHIC DATA INSTRUCTIONS: Complete one copy of this form for yourself and each member of your family, regardless of age, who will immigrate with you. Please print or type your answer to all questions. Questions that are Not Applicable should be so marked. If there is insufficient room on the form, answer on a separate sheet using the same numbers as appear on the form. Attach the sheet to this form. WARNING: Any false statement or concealment of a material fact may result in your permanent exclusion from the United States. This form (OF-230 PART I) is Part I of two parts which, together with Optional Form OF-230 PART II, constitute the complete Application for Immigrant Visa and Alien Registration. 1. FAMILY NAME FIRST NAME MIDDLE NAME SIKRI NARAIN DASS 2. OTHER NAMES USED OR BY WHICH KNOWN (If married woman, give maiden name) N/A 3. FULL NAME IN NATIVE ALPHABET (If Roman letters not used) NARAIN DASS SIKRI 4. DATE OF BIRTH 5. AGE 6. PLACE OF BIRTH (Day) (Month) (Year) (City or town) (Province) (Country) 1 12 1903 91 Kot Sultan PUNJAB PAKISTAN 7. NATIONALITY (If dual national, 8. SEX 9. MARITAL STATUS give both) Male Single (Never married) Married Widowed Divorced Separated INDIA Female Including my present marriage, I have been married 1 times. 10. PERSONAL DESCRIPTION 11. OCCUPATION a. Color of hair Grey C. Height 5'-8" Retired b. Color of eyes Brown d. Complexion Fair 12. MARKS OF IDENTIFICATION 13. PRESENT ADDRESS 157 Sector 14 Cut on right ear Faridabad 121007, Haryana India Telephone number: Home 8-282282 Office 14.
